#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_navigationagent2d.rst:19
msgid ""
"2D Agent that is used in navigation to reach a location while avoiding "
"static and dynamic obstacles. The dynamic obstacles are avoided using RVO"
" collision avoidance. The agent needs navigation data to work correctly. "
"This can be done by having the agent as a child of a :ref:`Navigation2D "
"<class_Navigation2D>` node, or using :ref:`set_navigation "
"<class_NavigationAgent2D_method_set_navigation>`. ``NavigationAgent2D`` "
"is physics safe."
msgstr ""

